Package: degradr
Type: Package
Title: Title: Estimating Remaining Useful Life with Linear Mixed Effects Models
Description: Provides tools to estimate the Remaining Useful Life (RUL) of degrading systems using mixed effects models. Supports both linear and exponential degradation models (the latter via a logarithmic transformation). Remaining Life Distributions (RLDs) are computed for new units via Bayesian updating, allowing in-situ predictive maintenance. Based on the methodology of Liu and Huang (2016) <doi:10.1109/TASE.2014.2349733>.
Version: 1.0.0
